snippet.title: CastleMiner Z Official Trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/253430/CastleMiner_Z/

Available now on Steam

CastleMiner Z is an online coop survival horror game in a block based environment. Travel with your  friends in a huge spanning and ever-changing world while defending yourself from the zombie hoard. Mine the world for resources, to craft the weapons that you will need to survive.
